  – Attention-augmented CNNs: Squeeze-Excite, CBAM, CoordAtt  
  – Hybrid Token-CNN: ConvMixer, PatchConv, LocalViT  
  – Pure Token: ViT, DeiT, CaiT  
  – Token-CNN Bridges: CMT, PVT, NesT  
  – Automatic Search: NASNet, AmoebaNet, ProxylessNAS  
  – Scale-agnostic Pyramids: FPN, HRNet, BiFPN  
  – Recurrent & Recursive: RCNN, RNN-Conv hybrids, ConvRNN  
  – Graph-based: GCN-Vision, Dynamic-Graph CNN  
  – MoE Vision: CondConv, Switch-Transformers  

• Some task-related Design Elements / Concept / Paradigm (illustrative, not exhaustive)  
  – Kernel variants: 3×3, 5×5, 7×7, depthwise, pointwise, group  
  – Expansion tricks: inverted bottleneck, squeeze-expand, Ghost  
  – Downsampling: stride-2 conv, max-pool, avg-pool, blur-pool  
  – Multi-scale branches: split-scale, Inception-style, fractal  
  – Dilation spectrum: 1,2,3, atrous pyramid  
  – Channel mixing: 1×1 conv, linear token mix, MLP-mixing  
  – Spatial mixing: conv, self-attn, local-attn, shift, circulant  
  – Positional cues: fixed sin-cos, learnable pos-emb, coord-conv  
  – Attention flavors: SE-scalar, channel-spatial, axial, criss-cross  
  – Tokenization: patchify, pixel-shuffle, learned embed tokens  
  – Aggregation heads: GAP-dense, classifier token, convolutional head  
  – Residual topology: basic, bottleneck, pre-act, anti-alias  
  – Skip density: plain, dense-connect, residual-in-residual, ladder  
  – Normalizations: Batch, Layer, Group, EvoNorm, Filter-Response  
  – Activation library: ReLU, Leaky, GELU, SiLU, Mish, PReLU  
  – Stochastic depth: per-block drop, layer-scale, path-drop  
  – Feature dropout: channel-drop, DropBlock, spatial-dropout  
  – Input augment: RandAugment, CutMix, MixUp, Cutout  
  – Representation mixing: manifold mixup, token mix, style mix  
  – Intermediate supervision: aux-heads, deep stem logits  
  – Loss couplings: label-smoothing, angular margin, focal, soft-target  
  – Parameter sharing: recurrent block reuse, weight tying  
  – Adaptive routing: gating, conditional conv, dynamic-width  
  – Width scaling: base_dim sweep, stage-wise width multiplier  
  – Depth scaling: repeat-count, compound scaling, nested repeats  
  – Micro search cells: NAS-cell, shuffle-cell, darts-cell  
  – Macro skeletons: stem-body-head, stage-pyramid, columnar  
  – Anti-overfit tricks: early dropout, label jitter, mix-style  
  – Weight regularizers: L2, orthogonal, spectral, weight decay  
  – Quantization-ready: fused-BN, integer-friendly ops, shift-add  
  – Memory savers: reversible blocks, checkpointing, group norm  
  – Efficiency extras: fused-MBConv, SqueezeNext, partial-conv  
  – Spatial bias add-ins: relative bias, coord-add, harmonic blocks  
  – Feature grafting: cross-stage attention, global context blocks  
  – Data-size aware: small-grid conv, stem stride-1, low-res tokens  
  – Ensemble-in-one: multi-head logits, multi-classifier gating  
  – Curriculum width: grow depth, progressive resizing, stage unfreeze  
  – Graphical soft labels: class hierarchy, similarity embedding  
  – Structural priors: symmetry tying, color channel grouping  
  – Learnable pooling: GEM, Lp-pool, gated-pool  
  – Head decoupling: class-specific batch norm, per-class routing  
  – Post-classifier rectification: temperature scaling, logit adjust  


